OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine and
OL,6,Fwarm evening with plenty of hazy
OL,7,Fsunshine, then dry and mostly clear
OL,8,Fovernight. Patchy low cloud and mist
OL,9,Fmay develop on coasts and hills later.
OL,10,FStaying rather warm in urban areas,
OL,11,Flocally much cooler in rural spots.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FAny fog quickly clearing to
OL,14,Fleave a mostly sunny day. Feeling much
OL,15,Fwarmer with temperatures rising to
OL,16,Fwell above the seasonal average.
OL,17,FSomewhat fresher in many coastal
OL,18,Fregions. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
